{"tid":559398,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(真係咁好心？)內地賣氣球母女不慎放走37個氣球　網民爭相認購","createTime":"2018-02-13T06:47:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T07:06:43.000Z","uid":15440,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6dcdf8a562d9995400d438b783b6f8309b97fce2","tid":559398,"uid":15440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:47:53.000Z","msg":"長沙一名年輕母親帶著女兒到街上賣氣球，但不小心把氣球全放走，並卡在電線杆上，一名路過的女士不忍母女血本無歸，在網上發起認購，結果37個氣球很快便全被認購。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n周五(9日)晚上，一對母女到街上賣氣球，但不小心鬆手放走氣球，氣球飄到電線杆上。母女十分焦急，向附近商舖求助，想借來長杆把氣球鈎下來。<br />\n<br />\n袁女士剛好路過，見母女沮喪地看著氣球，相當同情其遭遇，不忍她們血本無歸，遂向該母親提出，將氣球的錢付給她，惟母親婉拒袁女士好意。該批氣球共37個，每個售20元人民幣(約港元)，總售價700多元人民幣(約港元)。<br />\n<br />\n袁女士改為提議替她發起認購，<span style=\"color: red;\">網民每人買一個氣</span>球，當作把氣球放飛許願，母女願意接受。不到3分鐘，袁女士就收到<span style=\"color: red;\">500多個</span>「微信紅包」，她隨即給了<span style=\"color: red;\">720元現</span>金予母女，母女連聲感謝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n500x20 -720 = <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180212/s00004/1518430255627\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180212%2Fs00004%2F1518430255627&d=IC4%2BU%2FsjN3mjXxYTZGhUmEjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=52d7f9b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180212%2Fs00004%2F1518430255627&h=f6fecba0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180212/s00004/1518430255627</a>"},{"pid":"d5900143969d0dfb7cc548b29ead2e3fa603c004","tid":559398,"uid":20449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:49:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f78cb2e19550cfe9ff8f54cc1feb3a8a8d006602","tid":559398,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T06:51:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"86e438b4c0508155